            <div class="title">
                Prolongation Of Parliament Bill
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1942-09-30/debates/d2abc15e-005c-4091-b880-ffeac612a4e2/LocalElectionsAndRegisterOfElectors(TemporaryProvisions)Bill" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
