<div class="content-item" id="contribution-30fc0316-a0b0-4eef-bb78-2994c3d81b04">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-30fc0316-a0b0-4eef-bb78-2994c3d81b04">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
