<p class="">Can the right hon. Gentleman now tell us why they draw their salaries in that case?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-64a2540c-06f4-4c4f-9008-af5ef7543487" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
