                Mr. Brown
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-fb3923b7-26c7-43f4-b469-acbaabc90e28" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
