            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-c6dbe9a8-b20e-4729-8cf1-7f7505f0d6cc" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
