<p class="">I am a member of that committee. The report has not yet gone in, but it will be presented very shortly.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-40805536-e331-482e-b228-210ccb20184c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
