<p class="">Surely the hon. and gallant Member is more intelligent in his views than that. He does not deny that the Northern Ireland Government have taken away the rights normally exercised by the municipal authority in Belfast.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
