                Sir W. Allen
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-f1f102e1-d2e7-49be-87ac-718ccb1c46b9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
